<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="compromise-vi">compromise <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒmprəmaɪz/    美 /'kɑːmprəmaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>妥协；让步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He did not compromise easily, but was willing to accept any constructive advice for a worthy cause.
他不会轻易妥协，但是愿意为崇高的事业接受任何有建设性的建议。</p><footer>2016 江苏</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had to <strong>compromise with</strong> him <strong>on</strong> this point.
在这一点上我不得不对他让步。</p></div></div>